<p>
	<strong>Atsushi&nbsp;Inaba</strong>
	<table border="1" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#DEDEDE">
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" class="tableCell">President and Chief Executive Officer,&nbsp;Clover Studio, Capcom (Viewtiful Joe)</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" class="tableCell">Atsushi Inaba is president and CEO of Clover Studio Co., Ltd, an independent development house funded by Capcom Japan. Inaba oversees the company’s commitment to creating games with a bold and creative approach that will appeal to a variety of audiences.  In addition to managing the day-to-day operations, which support over 60 remarkable talents, he is also acting producer for titles that are currently in development including Viewtiful Joe series and Okami. 

Inaba brings to his position more than 12 years of game development experience. Prior to forming Clover Studio, Inaba served as a producer and general manager of Capcom Japan’s Production Studio 4, which developed award-winning and innovative franchises such as Steel Battalion and Viewtiful Joe.  Inaba began his career as a programmer for arcade manufacturers and joined Capcom in 1998 as a programmer for various projects. 
&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>										
